Interface AdaptationRequestInt

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AspectGeneration

    public interface AdaptationRequestInt
    This input interface is used by the rest of modules in the INTER-TRUST framework to request an adaptation in the aspects being applied for a particular application. This information is provided in terms of changing that need to be done on the security policies or on the security testing.
